\v 15 <a name="00202601500004">Сделай</a> для <a name="00202601500016" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁכָּן:000002:Tents">скинии</a> <a name="00202601500010" ll="SDBH:קֶרֶשׁ:000000:Parts: Tents" il="Realia:3.15.2.3.1a">рамы</a> из <a name="00202601500020" ll="SDBH:שִׁטָּה:000000:Plants" il="Flora:1.1a;Flora:1.1b;tb062205388;Flora0002;AcaciaThorns">акации</a>:
