\v 26 В <a name="00204002600016" ll="SDBH:אֹהֶל:000001:Tents" il="HK00223;LB00259;Realia:3.15.2b;Realia:3.15.2.3.6.4a;Realia:3.15.2.3.7;Realia:3.15.2.3.9">Шатре</a> <a name="00204002600018" ll="SDBH:מֹועֵד:000005:Tents">Встречи</a>, <a name="00204002600022">перед</a> <a name="00204002600026" ll="SDBH:פָּרֹכֶת:000000:Furnishings" il="Realia:3.14.1.6;il_tabernacle_holy_incense_veil_m30;mf110902489">завесой</a>, он поставил <a name="00204002600012" ll="SDBH:זָהָב:000000:Metals" il="Bolen00041;Bolen00050;adr1306212575;adr1006039110">золотой</a> <a name="00204002600008" ll="SDBH:מִזְבֵּחַ:000000:Cult Objects" il="HK00256;Realia:4.2.3;NBGmk20140519;NBGlo20140504a;NBGlo20140504b;NBGlo20140504c">жертвенник</a>
